    ${params}=          Create Dictionary   this_is_a_string=1  p2=2
    ${resp}=            GET  ${HTTP_LOCAL_SERVER}/anything
    ...                     params=this_is_a_string=1&p2=2
    Status Should Be    OK  ${resp}
    Dictionaries Should Be Equal  ${params}  ${resp.json()}[args]

